org.eclipse.scada.configuration.security

Interface Rule

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    LogonRule, ScriptRule, SignatureRule
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    LogonRuleImpl, RuleImpl, ScriptRuleImpl, SignatureRuleImpl

    public interface Rule
    A representation of the model object 'Rule'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Id
    • Id Filter
    • Action Filter
    • Type Filter
    • Filter Script

    See Also:
    SecurityPackage.getRule()
